<lb ed="L" n="0101a02"/><cb:div type="note"><entry><form>沌</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0101a0202" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">徒本切音囤混沌元氣未判也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>墾</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0101a0215" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">口很切音懇力治也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB04261">𨂲</g></term></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0101a0224" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">郎丁切<term rend="no_nor">跉</term><term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB04261">𨂲</g></term>行
<lb ed="L" n="0101a03"/>貌</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>苒</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0101a0303" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">而琰切荏苒猶展轉也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>祕</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0101a0313" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">兵媚切神也密也藏也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
